## 2. Definition
Contradiction repair is any process where:



\[
g_1 \cdot g_2 \rightarrow 0 \quad \text{or} \quad g_1 \cdot g_2 > 0
\]



Where:
- \( g_1, g_2 \in \nabla \mathcal{F} \) are opposing gradients  
- negative dot product indicates contradiction  
- zero or positive dot product indicates resolution or alignment  

Repair restores gradient coherence.

